ifold. It is conjectured that\nevery self-affine tile which is a manifold is a handlebody.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Feb 2014 22:39:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Apr 2015 16:41:21 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 9 Nov 2015 16:06:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-10"}
