ven frictional interface. We establish that the experimental determination\nof this interface property may be achieved by experimentally monitoring slip\npulses whose frequency content is rich enough.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Feb 2014 07:08:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-14"}
